   "weapons": "2 Pulse Laser Cannons (turret): Fire Control 2D, Space Range 1-3/12/25, Atmo Range 100-300/1.2/2.5 km, Damage 4D. 2 Retractable Firestorm Air-to-Ground Missile Racks (front, speeder scale, atmosphere only): Fire Control 2D, Atmo Range 100-250/400/800m, Damage 7D. Takes 1 round to deploy. 250 missiles per rack. Can fire singly or all at once (10D walker-scale).",
   "capsule": "Alliance SpecForce combat vessel used by Reekeene's Roughnecks against Moff Sakai in Thuris sector. Cargo bays replaced with weapons lockers, medical suite, and tactical briefing room with holotank and SpecForce Command comms link. Additional sublight drives, retractable missile racks on hinged wings, rear deployment hatch for commando exits. Credited with destroying 872 million tons of Imperial equipment including an orbital shipyard. Currently missing — believed adrift in space after Venom Guard SpecNav infiltration. Infamous in Imperial circles (Moderate law enforcement to recognize; Easy in Thuris sector — likely summary execution). Concealed data files contain sensitive Alliance military operations.",
